<%# 우측 드로어 상세 콘텐츠 — 닫기 + 헤더 + 하위(폴더)/구성요소 타임라인(리프). product 로컬 사용 %>
<div class="flex h-full min-h-0 flex-col bg-white">
  <%# 드로어 헤더: 브레드크럼 + 닫기 %>
  <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2 border-b border-line-soft px-5 py-3">
    <div class="min-w-0 truncate text-[13px]"><%= node_breadcrumb(product) %></div>
    <button type="button" data-action="detail-drawer#close" aria-label="닫기"
            class="shrink-0 rounded-lg p-1.5 text-line transition hover:bg-tint hover:text-ink">
      <%= ui_icon "x", size: 18 %>
    </button>
  </div>

  <div class="min-h-0 flex-1 overflow-auto px-5 py-4">
    <%# 제품 헤더 %>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-4">
      <div class="min-w-0">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <% if product.code.present? %>
            <span class="bg-cooa-gradient rounded-md px-2 py-0.5 text-[13px] font-bold text-white">[<%= product.code %>]</span>
          <% else %>
            <%= ui_icon "folder", size: 22, klass: "text-cooa" %>
          <% end %>
          <h1 class="min-w-0 break-words text-xl font-bold text-ink"><%= product.name %></h1>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-tint px-2 py-0.5 text-xs text-ink/70"><%= product.folder? ? "그룹" : product.product_type %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-5 gap-y-1 text-[13px] text-ink/80">
          <% if product.country.present? %><span>국가 · <b class="text-ink"><%= product.country_label %></b></span><% end %>
          <% if product.channel.present? %><span>채널 · <b class="text-ink"><%= product.channel %></b></span><% end %>
          <% if product.deadline %><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><%= ui_icon "calendar", size: 14 %> <%= product.deadline.strftime("%Y.%m.%d") %></span><% end %>
          <% if product.notion_url.present? %>
            <%= link_to product.notion_url, target: "_blank", rel: "noopener", class: "inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-cooa hover:underline" do %>
              <%= ui_icon "external", size: 14 %> Notion 기획문서
            <% end %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <% if product.product_members.any? %>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-4 gap-y-2">
          <% product.product_members.sort_by { |m| %w[designer pm ra scm].index(m.role) || 9 }.each do |pm| %>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
              <%= avatar(pm.user, size: 28) %>
              <div class="leading-tight">
                <div class="text-[12px] font-bold text-ink"><%= pm.user.name %></div>
                <div class="text-[10px] text-line"><%= pm.role_short %></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <%# 하위 항목 (폴더 노드) — 클릭 시 같은 드로어에서 펼침 %>
    <% if product.children.any? %>
      <h2 class="mb-2 mt-5 text-base font-bold text-ink">하위 항목</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <% product.children.each do |child| %>
          <%= link_to product_path(child), data: { turbo_frame: "detail", turbo_action: "advance" },
                class: "flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-line-soft bg-white p-3 shadow-sm hover:border-cooa" do %>
            <%= ui_icon(child.leaf? ? "doc" : "folder", size: 20, klass: "text-cooa") %>
            <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="truncate text-sm font-bold text-ink"><%= child.name %></span>
                <% if child.code.present? %><span class="text-[11px] text-line"><%= child.code %></span><% end %>
              </div>
              <div class="text-[12px] text-line">
                <% if child.leaf? %><%= [child.country_label, child.channel].compact.join(" · ") if child.country.present? %>
                <% else %><%= child.children.size %>개 하위<% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <%= ui_icon "caret", size: 16, klass: "-rotate-90 text-line" %>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <%# 구성요소 · 버전 타임라인 (리프 노드) %>
    <% if product.components.any? %>
      <div class="mb-3 mt-5 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-x-4 gap-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-ink">구성요소 · 버전</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-4 gap-y-1 text-[12px] text-line">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5"><%= version_chip("V", size: 18, active: true) %> 버전 클릭 = 인허가 스크리닝</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="flex h-5 w-5 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-line-soft text-line"><%= ui_icon "caret", size: 12 %></span> 변경사유 펼치기 · 비교</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-line-soft bg-white px-4 shadow-sm">
        <%= render partial: "products/component", collection: product.components.sort_by { |c| [c.position || 0, c.id] }, as: :component %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
